ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Useful course, hope they decide to include some regular assignments.
I recommend this course if the topics of treatment effects are of interest.
I would recommend this course in particular for students that have a reasonable understanding of basic methodology in econometrics.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I have got going thinking about an econometrics paper from end to end.
I obtained a good sense of various methodologies of estimations. Knowing these may help in the future to design researches.
